Hello, as an ALL-STAR host I strive to provide you with a magnificent experience. 🔥

All my vehicles are professionally maintained and the cleanest cars that you will find on Turo. When you choose any of our cars you not only pick the best but also you can rest assure you are choosing the best

We understand things happen, I try to be a flexible host and always work with my guest. Just ask! 
As an avid traveler myself alongside my wife, we get it... Airports are always a stressful time, we try to keep our process simple and worry free. If its's your first time and something isn't feeling right, just give me a call and we will do our best to help you!
If you'd like to receive any tips on places to go visit or how to work the vehicle, we are always available for you 24/7. 

👌We take our reservations extremely seriously👌
Complete Customer satisfaction is our mission that's why we provide much more than just a car.

Our commitment:

🚩We will never cancel your reservation.

🚩If you want to extend your trip and the current car is not available, we will do everything we can to provide you with a replacement.

🚩 Washed and cleaned cars. 

🚩 We only do contactless pickup, which makes it easier for both parties.

🚩 We always provide you with close to 90% charge.

🚩Delivery to SeaTac airport, home pick up and other locations.

🚩All our cars are instant booking if up choose to pick up at our home office, because we know time is precious.
    
    🌎Pre-paid charge or fuel level (return the car at any level)
    🌎Post trip cleaning fee (return the car hassle free)
 
    🌎Camping gear (sleeping bag, coolers and tent)
    
If there's an extra you wish and it's not on our list please let us know and we will add it. 

⚠️🚭🚭All our cars are NON-SMOKING🚭🚭⚠️
We will Immediately add a $200 charge to get the smoke out of the car 

🧴 Professionally CLEANED, SANITIZED, & DISINFECTED prior to every rental

 SE HABLA ESPAÑOL

Welcome to my fleet of professionally maintained and impeccably clean cars, the top choice for your Turo adventure! 🌟 Book with confidence and book instantly – because who has time to wait?

Why pick me as your car host?
✅ Ready for pickup or drop-off 7 AM to  10 PM - 365 days
✅ Flash your license, and your car is ready – no waiting around!
✅ Start your trip with a full tank of gas – no more stressful empty tanks!
✅ Our cars are clean and disinfected, ensuring a safe and enjoyable ride.
✅ Traveling with kids? We've got you covered with infant, baby, and booster seats for rent!
✅ Your satisfaction is guaranteed with every single rental – our priority is your happiness!
✅ All cars are available for instant booking – because time is of the essence!
✅ Our vehicles are well-maintained, thanks to our full-time mechanic on staff.
✅ Need a car ASAP? Book and be ready to roll with just a one-hour lead time.

I absolutely love what I do, and I'm thrilled to host your trip in Washington! 🚗✨ Check out my reviews, and let's make your Turo experience unforgettable! 🌈🏆
